Write a method maxLength that takes an ArrayList of 5 Strings as a parameter and that returns the length of the longest string in the list. 
If your method is passed an empty list, it should return 0.

 

Enter 5 Strings to store in arraylist:
pr
ogr
amr
node
s
Length of longest string in arraylist:4
   

Enter 5 Strings to store in arraylist:
hello
world
programr
java
php
Length of longest string in arraylist:8